1282
01:00:24.330 --> 01:00:26.332
TYLER PERRY:
Her gift and her singing

1283
01:00:26.415 --> 01:00:28.542
and the way she sings
and where it comes from.

1284
01:00:28.625 --> 01:00:30.085
her gut was born out of trauma.

1285
01:00:30.169 --> 01:00:31.837
-♪ In me. baby ♪
-♪ Yeah ♪

1286
01:00:31.920 --> 01:00:33.297
♪ Stay with... ♪

1287
01:00:33.380 --> 01:00:35.549
It’s like having a balloon
where you’re filling it

1288
01:00:35.632 --> 01:00:37.843
with trauma and pain and just so
much. so much. so much. so much.

1289
01:00:37.926 --> 01:00:39.261
You got to let it out.

1290
01:00:39.345 --> 01:00:41.263
And you can put
a pin in it and...

1291
01:00:41.347 --> 01:00:42.973
and blow up the whole world--

1292
01:00:43.057 --> 01:00:46.393
which-which Mary will do
if you really piss her off.

1293
01:00:46.477 --> 01:00:49.188
She will burn up the damn house
with her "in it to get you"

1294
01:00:49.271 --> 01:00:51.607
if you go at her.
and I. and I know that.

1295
01:00:51.690 --> 01:00:54.318
But-but to have that moment

1296
01:00:54.401 --> 01:00:56.945
where you take the edge of the
balloon and you let the air out

1297
01:00:57.029 --> 01:00:59.990
a little bit at a time
so you don’t destroy everything.

1298
01:01:00.074 --> 01:01:01.367
it’s almost primal.

1299
01:01:01.450 --> 01:01:04.244
It’s almost
the little girl crying out.

1300
01:01:04.328 --> 01:01:05.829
But it’s such a beautiful thing

1301
01:01:05.913 --> 01:01:07.414
because there’s
so much healing in it.

1302
01:01:07.498 --> 01:01:10.417
♪ Please. baby. take my hand ♪

1303
01:01:10.501 --> 01:01:13.587
♪ I don’t need another man ♪

1304
