Look at my little girl.

1312
01:01:33.273 --> 01:01:35.234
Oh. my God.

1313
01:01:35.317 --> 01:01:37.444
WOMAN: ...just the title track.
"My Life." I thought that was...

1314
01:01:37.528 --> 01:01:40.572
I know. The picture’s all fat.
and I look like Skeletor.

1315
01:01:40.656 --> 01:01:41.865
-No. you don’t.
-(laughs)

1316
01:01:41.949 --> 01:01:43.367
You’re so cute.

1317
01:01:43.450 --> 01:01:44.952
WOMAN: ...just about
what you were going through.

1318
01:01:45.035 --> 01:01:46.954
You look like
you’re giving her that eye.

1319
01:01:47.037 --> 01:01:48.831
WOMAN: ...but again.
running to your emotion.

1320
01:01:48.914 --> 01:01:51.291
Well. I wrote it
when I was in...

1321
01:01:51.375 --> 01:01:53.460
I was living--
I first moved to Jersey.

1322
01:01:53.544 --> 01:01:56.755
Uh. that’s when I started
the second album in summer.

1323
01:01:56.839 --> 01:01:59.925
And I wrote it
through just watching...

1324
01:02:00.926 --> 01:02:02.636
...even as I was little.

1325
01:02:02.719 --> 01:02:06.390
watching people. couples
or whatever go through...

1326
01:02:06.473 --> 01:02:09.268
Looking at my face. I probably
didn’t like the interviewer.

1327
01:02:09.351 --> 01:02:13.522
-Mm-hmm. -And. um. I didn’t want
to give her everything.

1328
01:02:13.605 --> 01:02:17.401
I didn’t want to tell her
what I was really dealing with.

1329
01:02:17.484 --> 01:02:19.236
because it was
none of her fucking business.

1330
01:02:19.319 --> 01:02:21.864
-And I was really.
really mean then. -(laughs)

1331
01:02:21.947 --> 01:02:25.033
So if it was some energy
that I picked up that was wrong.

1332
01:02:25.117 --> 01:02:27.536
I was. I-I... I withheld.

1333
01:02:27.619 --> 01:02:30.414
I didn’t want her to know where
all the shit really came from.

1334
01:02:30.497 --> 01:02:32.416
It was. "It’s none of
your fucking business."

1335
01:02:32.499 --> 01:02:34.668
-You understand?
-WOMAN: Wait. is it-- like what?

1336
01:02:34.751 --> 01:02:36.920
-Going through what. though?
-Whatever.

1337
01:02:37.004 --> 01:02:38.255
You know what I’m saying?

1338
01:02:38.338 --> 01:02:40.132
Whatever it may be.

1339
01:02:40.215 --> 01:02:42.634
MARY: That’s my child and
that’s who I protect. you know?

1340
01:02:42.718 --> 01:02:44.261
That-that girl right there

1341
01:02:44.344 --> 01:02:47.681
and little five-year-old Mary
I protect today.

1342
01:02:47.764 --> 01:02:49.683
-You know what I’m saying?
-WOMAN: I do.

1343
01:02:49.766 --> 01:02:51.018
Never mind.
You don’t understand.

1344
01:02:51.101 --> 01:02:52.394
(laughter)

1345
01:02:52.478 --> 01:02:54.980
LaTONYA:
Yeah. you told her the deal.

1346
01:02:55.063 --> 01:02:57.191
But deal with it and not pry.

1347
01:02:57.274 --> 01:02:59.485
-Just leading now a little
too deep. -LISATH: Wow.

1348
01:02:59.568 --> 01:03:00.986
Wow.

1349
01:03:02.821 --> 01:03:06.825
I’ve always had a thing
where my intuition was strong.

1350
01:03:06.909 --> 01:03:11.163
and it would make me
go into a pr-protection mode.

1351
01:03:11.246 --> 01:03:15.042
And that’s what I’m doing there.
because I didn’t know I was me.

1352
01:03:16.418 --> 01:03:19.421
-Damn. that shit make me
want to cry. -Mm.

1353
01:03:19.505 --> 01:03:20.714
I didn’t know I was me.

1354
01:03:20.797 --> 01:03:23.717
I didn’t know I was
this Mary J. Blige

1355
01:03:23.800 --> 01:03:25.385
that was gonna have
this much courage.

1356
01:03:25.469 --> 01:03:27.095
that was gonna do
all these things.

1357
01:03:27.179 --> 01:03:30.474
I didn’t know I was me.
so I guess that happens

1358
01:03:30.557 --> 01:03:32.851
when you grow up
in an environment

1359
01:03:32.935 --> 01:03:34.937
where little girls are not safe.

1360
01:03:36.271 --> 01:03:37.814
Little girls are not safe
and you...

1361
01:03:37.898 --> 01:03:40.025
-Yeah. it’s just instincts.
yeah. -Yeah.

1362
01:03:40.108 --> 01:03:42.611
And that’s why my gut is God.

1363
01:03:42.694 --> 01:03:44.571
♪ ♪

1364
01:03:44.655 --> 01:03:47.199
I didn’t know I was me.

1365
01:03:47.282 --> 01:03:50.661
But I was me. That’s why
I was able to do what I did.

1366
01:03:50.744 --> 01:03:53.622
I was always this person.

1367
01:03:53.705 --> 01:03:55.332
Just didn’t know it.

1368
01:03:57.543 --> 01:04:01.463
It’s about you sitting
and knowing that.

1369
01:04:01.547 --> 01:04:04.007
in your gut. there’s God.

1370
01:04:09.179 --> 01:04:11.306
God is love.

1371
01:04:11.390 --> 01:04:16.478
God is you making decisions
on what-what do you want to do.

1372
01:04:16.562 --> 01:04:18.897
what you want to be.

1373
01:04:18.981 --> 01:04:20.607
You know. I--
even if I’m afraid.

1374
01:04:20.691 --> 01:04:24.361
I got to keep moving afraid.
as long as I get out there.

1375
01:04:24.444 --> 01:04:27.948
And once you. you know.
pass the fear threshold.

1376
01:04:28.031 --> 01:04:30.742
it’s over. game over. you know?

1377
01:04:30.826 --> 01:04:32.452
You can do anything.

