1407
01:05:49.529 --> 01:05:51.323
-XENOS SR.: Right. -You know.
I really wanted to be happy.

1408
01:05:51.406 --> 01:05:53.533
Everything I wanted to be. I was
like. "I want to be happy."

1409
01:05:53.617 --> 01:05:54.951
-LaTONYA: Mm-hmm.
