1412
01:05:59.206 --> 01:06:00.415
-Yeah. -Right.
-Wow.

1413
01:06:00.499 --> 01:06:02.918
What I realize
at this stage in my life.

1414
01:06:03.001 --> 01:06:06.380
it’s not for me
to go through these things

